            <h3>Privacy Policy Changes</h3>
            <p>Although most changes are likely to be minor, Holmwell Software may change its Privacy Policy from time to time, and in Holmwell Software’s sole discretion. Holmwell Software encourages visitors to frequently check this page for any changes to its Privacy Policy. If you have a CircleBlvd.org account, you should also check your circle’s dashboard for alerts to these changes. Your continued use of this site after any change in this Privacy Policy will constitute your acceptance of such change.</p>        

